name: unchainet
desc: Unchainet is a decentralized heterogeneous cloud network designed by a team of core developers with 75+ years of combined experience including extensive experience in cloud computing. Unchainet's platform targets the niche market for dApp developers and cloud computing users. Unlike existing distributed cloud solutions, Unchainet's application layer sits on our native blockchain making it both an IaaS/PaaS protocol. Our reputation blockchain allows users to access quality providers and allows reliable sellers to seamlessly monetize their server grade computing resources.
